comment: Casspi (SAC) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Sefolosha (ATL) that does not affect his driving layup attempt.
Horford (ATL) maintains legal guarding position as he contests Cousins' (SAC) shot attempt.
Cousins (SAC) moves his pivot foot. The official is looking for any illegal contact on the shot attempt and does not pick up the pivot foot.
Horford (ATL) makes a legal move to the basket.
Casspi (SAC) legally contests Sefolosha's (ATL) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Cousins (SAC) clamps the arm of Millsap (ATL), affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Millsap (ATL) firms up as he sets the screen on McLemore (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Horford (ATL) sets the screen on Cauley-Stein (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Rondo (SAC) and Millsap (ATL) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.
Rondo (SAC) maintains legal guarding position and cleanly strips the ball from Millsap (ATL) on his driving layup attempt.

After communicating with the Replay Center, there was conclusive video evidence that showed that Millsap (ATL) was the last player to touch the ball prior to it going OOB. The ruling on the court was overturned and Sacramento was awarded possession.
Rondo (SAC) sets the screen on Horford (ATL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Horford (ATL) maintains legal guarding position on Cousins' (SAC) driving layup attempt.
Millsap (ATL) makes contact with Cauley-Stein's (SAC) arm, affecting his ability to secure the loose ball.
Horford (ATL) and Cousins (SAC) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.
Cousins (SAC) sets the hand-off screen on Schroder (ATL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Cauley-Stein (SAC) maintains legal guarding position as Millsap (ATL) loses the ball on his own at the start of the drive.
Horford (ATL) sets the screen on Casspi (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Collison (SAC) and Korver (ATL) briefly engage and separate during an inbounds play.
Schroder (ATL) attempts a take foul on Collison (SAC) but does not make contact with him.
